## Technical Debt Checklist

| Area | Indicator | Action |
|---|---|---|
| Type Coverage | `mypy --strict` errors > 0 | Fix all type errors |
| Duplication | Similar code in 3+ locations | Extract to shared utility |
| Complexity | Function > 50 lines | Split into smaller functions |
| Dependencies | Unused imports | Remove and update `pyproject.toml` |
| Tests | Coverage < 80% | Add missing test cases |
| Documentation | Public API without docstring | Add docstrings |

