## Epic Workflow Position

The Refactor Agent runs **after Coding Agent** completes all tasks in an epic:

1. ✅ Coding Agent — Implementation complete
2. **🔄 Refactor Agent — You are here**
3. ⬜ Testing Agent — Next
4. ⬜ Docs Agent — Final

### Handoff Checklist

Before handing off to Testing Agent:
- [ ] All Pydantic models use `strict=True`
- [ ] No duplicate LLM routing code
- [ ] Output sanitization applied consistently
- [ ] AgentResultEnvelope schema preserved
- [ ] Backend verification gate passed: `uv run ruff check backend && uv run ruff format backend && uv run mypy backend && uv run pytest`

